She looked at Land Mine. "I;m not popping anyone. And you won't get 
pooped just because you make a mistake in your speach.  Besides, as 
far as I'm concerned, you haven't done anything to get popped over 
for," she paused, "except for cutting on yourself.  You cut on 
yourself and I will pop you. Got it.  No more self abuse unless I say 
so, got it? Good. Now, How is your arm feeling, it should be feeling 
better." she smiled and chuckled, "But no more hurting yourself.  
Your too good for that. OK?"
